OL,6, I remember when Ceefax opened all six  
OL,7, magazines in Nov 1989. It had Breakfast
OL,8, Daytime and Evening editions. In the   
OL,9, previous month, C4 subtitled a whole   
OL,10, day's programming, which was novel back
OL,11, then. I convinced mum I had a belly    
OL,12, ache and stayed home from school.      
OL,14, There was talk about the IBA selling   
OL,15, some lines on the VBI in 1989, I didn't
OL,16, get it then. but in 1991, it was       
OL,17, announced Oracle had lost the franchise
OL,19, For an 11 year old, I did my best to   
OL,20, make sense of it all. Was only until I 
OL,21, grew up and realised what had happened.
