OL,6, It became apparent that Oracle was to  
OL,7, close at midnight of 31 Dec 1992. I    
OL,8, observed the closedown process.        
OL,10, I watched Teletext UK turn on their    
OL,11, service, which took about 40 minutes to
OL,12, get it fully working. I frantically    
OL,13, checked all of their test pages until  
OL,14, their new service slowly woke up.      
OL,16, By then I turned 13. What with the     
OL,17, London TV switchover to Carlton and    
OL,18, a new era for Teletext, this was a     
OL,19, milestone for me to move on into my    
OL,20, teenage years.                         
