OL,6, Oracle really was a means for me to    
OL,7, connect with the outside world and     
OL,8, access a wealth of information.        
OL,9, I was interested in horoscopes, TV     
OL,10, listings, news and weather, articles   
OL,11, for the young and what's at the cinema.
OL,13, Speaking for my childhood, Oracle was a
OL,14, reader-friendly service. With its own  
OL,15, soul, I was sad to watch it closedown. 
OL,16, It signified the start of my teenage   
OL,17, years, which meant I got out more and  
OL,18, discovered cars and girls (scrap cars -
OL,19, I preferred home electronics actually).
