OL,7, pages on the Internet, I learned that  
OL,8, SVHS tape recordings were good enough  
OL,9, for teletext retrieval. Those were the 
OL,10, early days of teletext archaeology.    
OL,12, Who would have thought: today I can    
OL,13, write my own set of teletext pages and 
OL,14, send it to a Raspberry Pi for my TV.   
OL,15, This was an old ambition of mine.      
